Additionally, the paper discusses the relationship between MDL and Bayes modeling, which suggests that it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The paper also mentions the calculation of marginals and conditionals, which are concepts related to Data Structures (cs.DS) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses fast computation, which could also place it in the Computational Complexity (cs.CC) sub-category.
